    Interface Description
    AntProjectCookie
    Cookie containing the state of an Ant Project.
    AntProjectCookie.ParseStatus
    Extended cookie permitting queries of parse status.
    ElementCookie Deprecated
    Not currently used in Ant module UI.
    IntrospectionCookie Deprecated
    No longer useful in new UI.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AntTargetExecutor
    Executes an Ant target or list of targets asynchronously inside NetBeans.
    AntTargetExecutor.Env
    Class describing the environment in which the Ant target will be executed.
    IntrospectedInfo
    Represents Ant-style introspection info for a set of classes.

Package org.apache.tools.ant.module.api Description

Examination and execution of Ant build scripts. Few modules outside of the Ant module suite will need to use this package.
